<li class="txtMainBlack">Entrepreneurial Scotland</li>
</ul>
<p class="txtMainBlack"><strong>Queen Margaret University Converge Challenge alumni include: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="txtMainBlack">2015: 2 QMU alumni made it onto the shortlist award categories.</li>
